INSERT INTO `ServiceScope` (`ServiceScopeID`,`ServiceScopeCategory`,`ServiceScopeName`,`CreatedBy`,`CreatedTimestamp`,`UpdatedBy`,`UpdatedTimestamp`,`ServiceElementID`,`ServiceScopeDescription`,`Active`,`ServiceElementDefaultValue`) VALUES (1,'Application Management','Project Management Office','Admin',now(),'',now(),1,'Project Management Office deals with overall coordination of the projects belonging to a program. It ensures to successfully meet all objectives in terms of scope, time, cost and quality. Additionally, it deals with managing client meetings, reporting and communication, escalation path, acceptance tracking and reporting, change control, quality management, risk/ issue management (limited to the project/program execution scope).Service Desk function includes provide a single point of contact through Vendor provided toll free numbers (where possible), e-mail addresses and web access via a web-enabled interface, as approved by client, Support for planned contract volume overflow i.e. to provide support for handling increased contact volumes resulting from planned business initiatives and new programs, Data recording & retention, Provide on going maintenance support for web-based portal for functions including: reporting Incidents, user self-help information, password reset, and self-heal etc, Level1 Service Desk support (e.g. Incident detection, recording and reporting), Record and classify Service Requests, Provide reporting requirement support by design, develop, maintain and deliver Service Desk reports as approved by client','Y',null);
